31
00:01:39,916 --> 00:01:41,458
I don't think...

32
00:01:41,541 --> 00:01:43,291
[LEOS]
Hey, sweetie.

33
00:01:43,375 --> 00:01:45,875
We have wedding
plans to discuss.

34
00:01:45,958 --> 00:01:47,583
Care to come with me?

35
