39
00:02:02,333 --> 00:02:03,708
[RUMIA]
No!

40
00:02:03,791 --> 00:02:04,791
Rumia?

41
00:02:06,583 --> 00:02:08,416
[RUMIA]
You can't do that.

42
00:02:08,500 --> 00:02:09,541
Yeah, but...

43
00:02:17,333 --> 00:02:19,125
[RUMIA]
Please, be patient.

44
00:02:19,208 --> 00:02:22,208
I'm sure Professor Radars
will think of something.

45
00:02:22,291 --> 00:02:23,791
But Glenn is gone.

46
00:02:23,875 --> 00:02:26,708
Who knows where he is...
or if he'll be back.

47
00:02:29,208 --> 00:02:30,750
[RUMIA]
I tried to ask Sisti about it

48
00:02:30,833 --> 00:02:32,958
when she came home that night,

49
00:02:33,041 --> 00:02:36,166
but all she would say is
that she's marrying Leos.

50
00:02:36,250 --> 00:02:38,375
[SISTINE]
Just leave me alone, okay?

51
00:02:38,458 --> 00:02:39,625
Sisti...

52
00:02:46,500 --> 00:02:48,083
What the hell do you want?

53
00:02:49,375 --> 00:02:50,666
Rumia?

54
00:02:50,750 --> 00:02:53,333
Professor, if we don't
do something, Sisti will...

55
00:02:54,166 --> 00:02:56,583
[RUMIA] I told Professor
Radars everything I knew--

56
00:02:56,666 --> 00:02:58,500
everything that had happened.

57
00:02:58,583 --> 00:02:59,583
And then...

58
00:03:01,958 --> 00:03:03,291
I've got this.

59
00:03:04,208 --> 00:03:06,458
[RUMIA] Right after that,
he went to Re=L

60
00:03:06,541 --> 00:03:09,208
and told her that
she should stay with me.

61
00:03:09,291 --> 00:03:11,416
Then he just disappeared.

62
00:03:13,708 --> 00:03:15,125
[RUMIA]
It'll be all right.

63
