73
00:03:46,291 --> 00:03:47,416
[SISTINE]
Don't worry.

74
00:03:47,500 --> 00:03:49,750
I'm sure someday
you'll get to wear one

75
00:03:49,833 --> 00:03:52,041
of your own.

76
00:03:52,125 --> 00:03:53,625
Hey, Sisti...

77
00:03:53,708 --> 00:03:56,708
The ceremony's about to start,
so you should go find a seat.

78
00:03:58,875 --> 00:04:00,041
[RUMIA]
Sisti.

79
00:04:05,375 --> 00:04:07,208
[SISTINE crying]

80
00:04:07,291 --> 00:04:09,583
[PRIEST 12A]
Do you, Leos Kleitos,

81
00:04:09,666 --> 00:04:11,666
take this woman to be your wife,

82
00:04:11,750 --> 00:04:14,750
to have and to hold,
from this day forward,

83
