for better or for worse...

84
00:04:16,333 --> 00:04:19,000
[WENDY] There's not a single
person on the groom's side.

85
00:04:19,083 --> 00:04:20,916
That's not weird to anyone?

86
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,750
[PRIEST 12A]
...to love and to cherish,

87
00:04:22,833 --> 00:04:25,625
until death do you part?

88
00:04:25,708 --> 00:04:26,875
I do.

89
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:31,125
[LEOS] Now let's talk about
your friend Rumia Tingel's

90
00:04:31,208 --> 00:04:32,666
real name and power.

91
00:04:32,750 --> 00:04:35,083
And that science experiment,
Re=L Rayford.

92
00:04:35,166 --> 00:04:36,625
Do you care enough
to do what it takes

93
00:04:36,708 --> 00:04:37,750
to save them?

94
00:04:40,458 --> 00:04:42,000
I do.

95
00:04:42,083 --> 00:04:44,000
[PRIEST 12A]
You may now kiss the bride.

96
00:04:55,791 --> 00:04:59,333
[GLENN] Get your filthy
peter clamps away from her!

97
00:05:01,041 --> 00:05:03,458
I object to this marriage!

98
00:05:03,541 --> 00:05:04,916
Was waiting for you
to get to that part,

99
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,916
but you skipped right over it!

100
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:10,000
And I sure as hell
ain't gonna hold my peace!

101
00:05:10,083 --> 00:05:11,375
Suck smoke!

102
00:05:12,375 --> 00:05:13,583
--Nice!
--Awesome!

103
00:05:13,666 --> 00:05:15,125
[WENDY]
I knew he'd come!

104
00:05:15,208 --> 00:05:17,583
Re=L, protect Rumia!

105
00:05:17,666 --> 00:05:18,958
I'm on it.

106
00:05:19,041 --> 00:05:20,541
Oh, wow!

107
00:05:20,625 --> 00:05:22,833
[GLENN]
You may now kiss my ass!

108
00:05:22,916 --> 00:05:27,333
[GROUP cheering]

109
00:05:27,416 --> 00:05:29,291
[SISTINE]
Let go of me this instant!

110
00:05:29,375 --> 00:05:31,791
I mean it!
Put me down, right now!

111
00:05:31,875 --> 00:05:33,458
This is no picnic
for me, either.

112
00:05:33,541 --> 00:05:35,791
Y'know, you're a lot
heavier than you look.

113
00:05:35,875 --> 00:05:36,875
There.

114
00:05:36,958 --> 00:05:38,375
[SISTINE]
You've ruined everything!

115
00:05:38,458 --> 00:05:41,916
Take me back,
I have to marry Leos!

116
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,333
If I don't, then...

117
00:05:43,416 --> 00:05:44,583
Lemme guess.

118
00:05:44,666 --> 00:05:46,791
He was using Rumia
to threaten you?

119
00:05:48,416 --> 00:05:51,541
Yeah, I figured it had
to be something like that.

120
00:05:51,625 --> 00:05:52,916
Then you just left me.

121
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:55,250
Where have you been
all this time?

122
00:05:55,333 --> 00:05:56,791
I thought...

123
00:05:56,875 --> 00:05:58,333
I thought you'd...

124
00:05:58,416 --> 00:05:59,333
Sorry.

125
00:05:59,416 --> 00:06:00,625
Got held up.

126
00:06:02,375 --> 00:06:04,166
[GLENN] After Rumia
told me what was going on,

127
00:06:04,250 --> 00:06:07,750
I tried thinking of ways
I could bring you back.

128
00:06:07,833 --> 00:06:11,791
Only thing I knew for sure was
I'd be the one on the losing end

129
00:06:11,875 --> 00:06:14,875
if I didn't take
the fight seriously.

130
00:06:14,958 --> 00:06:16,083
That was it.

131
00:06:26,208 --> 00:06:29,125
[GLENN] Feels like I'm
back in the old days.

132
00:06:29,208 --> 00:06:31,041
Wonder how well this
little toy of mine'll

133
00:06:31,125 --> 00:06:32,208
work on him.

134
00:06:34,541 --> 00:06:35,875
Well, regardless,

135
00:06:35,958 --> 00:06:37,541
I just need to lure
Leos out to where I have

136
00:06:37,625 --> 00:06:40,083
the upper hand,
and then kick his ass.

137
00:06:41,833 --> 00:06:45,291
[GLENN] So, what do you
think Leos's end game is?

138
00:06:45,375 --> 00:06:47,166
I've been wracking my brain
trying to figure it out,

139
00:06:47,250 --> 00:06:49,500
but nothing really jumps at me.

140
00:06:49,583 --> 00:06:51,625
Best I could come up with
is that he loves you so much,

141
00:06:51,708 --> 00:06:53,416
he'd do anything,
no matter how bonkers,

142
00:06:53,500 --> 00:06:54,875
just to make you his.

143
00:06:56,375 --> 00:06:58,375
No, that's not it.

144
00:06:58,458 --> 00:07:00,250
I realized it that night.

145
00:07:00,333 --> 00:07:03,500
That man doesn't love me at all.

146
00:07:03,583 --> 00:07:07,166
He was cold.
A completely different person.

147
00:07:07,250 --> 00:07:08,166
It was scary.

148
00:07:08,250 --> 00:07:09,708
A different person, huh?

149
00:07:09,791 --> 00:07:12,416
[ADDICTS groaning]

150
00:07:13,833 --> 00:07:14,750
[SISTINE]
Professor?

151
00:07:14,833 --> 00:07:16,375
[GLENN]
Terminal addicts?

152
00:07:17,291 --> 00:07:20,541
[GLENN] But why is Angel's Dust
starting to show up again now?

153
00:07:22,333 --> 00:07:25,083
Uh... this is bad, isn't it?

154
00:07:27,500 --> 00:07:31,000
[ADDICTS groaning]

155
00:07:31,083 --> 00:07:32,833
--Get back.
--Everyone, back!

156
00:07:34,458 --> 00:07:35,416
Now.

157
00:07:37,333 --> 00:07:39,375
[ADDICTS groaning, growling]

158
00:07:42,250 --> 00:07:43,708
Sorry we're late.

159
00:07:44,666 --> 00:07:46,791
Re=L, keep everyone safe.

160
00:07:46,875 --> 00:07:48,291
Leave this to us.

161
00:07:48,375 --> 00:07:49,541
--Go, now!
--[WENDY] Okay!

162
00:07:49,625 --> 00:07:51,000
[CECIL]
Don't have to tell me twice!

163
00:07:51,083 --> 00:07:52,166
Are you coming?

164
00:07:52,250 --> 00:07:53,458
All right, let's go!

165
00:07:53,541 --> 00:07:54,500
Okay!

166
00:07:56,333 --> 00:07:57,875
Well, men?

167
00:07:57,958 --> 00:07:59,208
Let's do this.

168
00:07:59,291 --> 00:08:00,291
Right!

169
00:08:01,416 --> 00:08:03,916
[ADDICTS groaning]

170
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:05,166
Don't move!

171
00:08:06,083 --> 00:08:06,958
Damn it!

172
00:08:07,041 --> 00:08:08,916
They got us trapped.

173
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:10,166
But why?

174
00:08:10,250 --> 00:08:12,333
What's wrong with these people?

175
00:08:12,416 --> 00:08:13,833
[GLENN] At this point,
they're basically just

176
00:08:13,916 --> 00:08:15,041
dead flesh-puppets,

177
00:08:15,125 --> 00:08:17,166
blindly following
their master's orders.

178
00:08:17,250 --> 00:08:19,875
But never mind that. Go!

179
00:08:19,958 --> 00:08:21,291
Just get outta here!

180
00:08:21,375 --> 00:08:22,916
I can't deal with these
burnouts and babysit you

181
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:23,833
at the same time!

182
00:08:23,916 --> 00:08:25,583
Oh, don't you worry about me!

183
00:08:25,666 --> 00:08:28,208
I can take care of myself,
thank you very much!

184
00:08:28,291 --> 00:08:30,083
Pay heed, great wind... 

185
00:08:33,458 --> 00:08:34,916
[GLENN]
Rush forth, wind!

186
00:08:35,666 --> 00:08:37,416
[GLENN]
Rush and blow through...

187
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,666
[ADDICT 12B yelling]

188
00:08:42,958 --> 00:08:44,083
[GLENN]
...piercing them!

189
00:08:51,125 --> 00:08:52,333
[GLENN]
White cat!

190
00:08:52,416 --> 00:08:53,833
Don't just stand
there lookin' pretty!

191
00:08:53,916 --> 00:08:54,708
Let's go!

192
00:08:54,791 --> 00:08:56,333
[ADDICTS growling]

193
00:09:00,916 --> 00:09:02,291
[GLENN]
Thunder sprites...

194
00:09:02,375 --> 00:09:03,041
[ADDICT 12A yelps]

195
00:09:03,125 --> 00:09:04,583
[SISTINE gasps]

196
00:09:04,666 --> 00:09:07,625
[GLENN] ...pay heed and strike
with your... electric shock!

197
00:09:07,708 --> 00:09:09,958
[ADDICT 12G choking]

198
00:09:10,041 --> 00:09:11,000
No!

199
00:09:12,291 --> 00:09:13,750
[GLENN]
Hey, get a grip!

200
00:09:13,833 --> 00:09:14,625
This way!

201
00:09:14,708 --> 00:09:17,083
[ADDICTS groaning]

202
00:09:17,166 --> 00:09:18,541
[GLENN]
Damn it!

203
00:09:18,625 --> 00:09:21,750
I can't help but think we're
just being herded by Leos.

204
00:09:21,833 --> 00:09:24,458
Is he trying to
ensnare white cat?

205
00:09:24,541 --> 00:09:26,041
Like they did with her?

206
00:09:27,625 --> 00:09:28,625
[GLENN]
Sara!

207
00:09:32,333 --> 00:09:33,750
[GLENN]
You bastards!

208
00:09:41,333 --> 00:09:42,125
[GLENN]
That's it!

209
00:09:42,208 --> 00:09:44,458
That's what this is about!

210
00:09:44,541 --> 00:09:46,125
That son of a bitch!

211
00:09:46,208 --> 00:09:47,666
I can't let him do it!

212
00:09:47,750 --> 00:09:51,500
If I half-ass it this time,
I'll lose her again.

213
00:09:51,583 --> 00:09:54,750
Remember, you were an
Imperial Court Mage, damn it!

214
00:09:54,833 --> 00:09:57,583
[ADDICTS yelling]

215
00:10:01,541 --> 00:10:03,666
[SISTINE]
I'm.. so scared...

216
00:10:04,875 --> 00:10:07,583
White cat! Behind you!

217
00:10:07,666 --> 00:10:08,708
Son of a... !

218
00:10:11,583 --> 00:10:13,250
[SISTINE gasps]

219
00:10:13,333 --> 00:10:14,875
[GLENN]
White cat, are you all right?

220
00:10:14,958 --> 00:10:16,541
Get away from me!

221
00:10:20,333 --> 00:10:23,000
[GLENN] You're afraid
of me now, aren't you?

222
00:10:26,375 --> 00:10:27,791
[GLENN]
Sorry.

223
00:10:27,875 --> 00:10:30,458
[SISTINE]
Just... give me a minute.

224
00:10:30,541 --> 00:10:33,083
[clapping]

225
00:10:33,166 --> 00:10:34,958
[LEOS]
Bravo. [laughs]

226
00:10:35,041 --> 00:10:36,916
Jolly good show, Glenn.

227
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:37,916
Bastard!

228
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,916
You can drop the Leos disguise!

229
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:41,208
Well done.

230
00:10:41,291 --> 00:10:42,916
I thought you might figure
out my true identity

231
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:44,708
sooner or later.

232
00:10:44,791 --> 00:10:46,500
That man isn't Leos.

233
00:10:46,583 --> 00:10:48,416
He's former Imperial
Court Mage Corps

234
00:10:48,500 --> 00:10:53,125
Executioner Number Eleven,
Justice, Jatice Lowfan.

235
00:10:53,208 --> 00:10:54,666
You look surprised.

236
00:10:54,750 --> 00:10:57,000
Didn't think I was
still alive, did ya?

237
00:11:00,208 --> 00:11:02,375
Wait. Where is Leos?

238
00:11:02,458 --> 00:11:03,375
Tell me!

239
00:11:03,458 --> 00:11:05,416
Oh, that pompous little turd?

240
00:11:05,500 --> 00:11:08,000
